needDefaultMap: Need to set a default grid map
allowAdjust: Whether adjustments are allowed in talent review activity
fromSmalltoLarge: Please enter the underlined standard values in ascending order
selectGridTemplate: Please select the matrix grid template first
ratingsTips: If the Calculation Type is 'Grade', the Ratings allows multiple values to be entered in a section, with multiple values separated by commas. For example, if the configuration is 'A, B', then employees with scores of A or B will fall in this section.
